# Balloon Mission TODO

Short description of current focus and context for this project.

## Conventions

- Use `- [ ]` for open tasks and `- [x]` for done tasks.
- Prefix tasks with component tags like `[main]`, `[spectrometer]`, `[pressure]`, `[gyro]`, `[temp]`, `[infra]`, `[editor]`, `[bash]`.
- Optional metadata at the end: `@you yyyy-mm-dd ~estimate`.

