Example `bin/go` script:

modularize all functions and let each create a data file in the appropiate folder.


systemd for chopper:
[Unit]
Description=Chopper UDP Server
After=network-online.target
Wants=network-online.target

[Service]
ExecStart=/usr/bin/python3 /home/pi/src/chopper_udp_server.py --port 5126 --pin 12
WorkingDirectory=/home/pi/src
User=pi
Group=pi
Restart=on-failure
RestartSec=2s

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
